      <title>当AI遇上混乱：为什么你的组织架构才是真正的瓶颈</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1315/insights/article-20250624081004171-0/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Jun 2025 08:10:04 +0800</pubDate>
